Some of the playground games that children play at our school are;
Catch, Elastics, Skipping, On the mountain, I'm a little bumper car, Creepy mouse, Adventure games.
{RULES FOR CREEPY MOUSE { Somebody is the cat and they stand with their back to the other people who are standing in a line about 3 metres away. The people walk up to the cat slowly. After a few seconds the cat turns around and if the cat sees a person move they have to go back to start. The first person to reach the cat shouts{CREEPY MOUSE.
